column inside a row
you can use  ***col*** class , and bootstrap will do the calculation for the size

if you want to specific a size for the column
-- by using ***col-number*** , each row has 12 units size to manage it
If you do not specify a size for the last column, it will be auto

-- must often we use variable with contact
by using the breakpoint with the size of column

